Comment: 0,0:03:58.96,0:03:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,op
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 没有 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 没有 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,找到啦！帐篷！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好像不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这样怎么能露营呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,富士山…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00645F60\bord2.5\3c&H00FFFFFF\blur\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs50\b1\frz354.8\pos(718.4,358)}凛今天好像在这里露营哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是齐藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.47,0:01:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要开车出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,确实要啦…你带了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,捎我一程嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢姐姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,办手续是在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去喽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,说是要收钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,凛～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们来做火锅吧！
